# FILE: studentDashboard/academicProfile/academicProfile.desc
# ROLE: Student Digital Identity & Growth Hub
# ROUTE: /dashboard (index)
# ACCOUNT: Student only — redirects Business/Admin to their respective dashboards
# THEME: Dark · #0F1828 surface · #6366F1 accent · gradient XP bar

## DESIGN SYSTEM (matches current app)
- LAYOUT: max-w-7xl mx-auto · px-6 sm:px-10 lg:px-16
- CARDS: bg-[#0F1828] · border border-[#1E2D45] · rounded-2xl/3xl
- ACCENT: gradient-text on values · gradient-bg on primary buttons

## 1. IDENTITY HEADER (Top Fold)
- AVATAR: large rounded-full gradient-bg placeholder with emoji or photo
  - GLOW: shadow-[#6366F1]/20 — increases to /40 if isVerified === true
- NAME: text-xl font-bold text-[#F1F5F9]
- STATUS: "السنة الرابعة · هندسة معلوماتية" — text-[#94A3B8]
- VERIFIED BADGE: "✅ طالب موثّق" — bg-[#6366F1]/15 · border-[#6366F1]/25 · text-[#818CF8]
  - Shown only when isVerified === true
- PENDING BADGE: "🕒 في انتظار التحقق" — amber style — shown when isVerified === false
- MOTTO: "Challenge Every Day." — italic gradient-text

## 2. XP ENGINE (Gamification Bar)
- XP BAR: h-3 bg-[#162032] rounded-full → filled with gradient-bg
- LABELS: "Level 4 — Academic Researcher" + "1,600 / 2,500 XP" (muted)
- PROGRESS: calculated as (currentXP / nextLevelXP) * 100%
- LEVEL FORMULA: Level = √(XP ÷ 100)

## 3. QUICK STATS (2×2 Grid)
- CARD STYLE: bg-[#162032] · rounded-2xl · border border-[#1E2D45] · text-center
- STATS: تحميلات المكتبة · دورات مكتملة · طلبات المتجر · خدمات نشطة
- VALUE: text-2xl font-black gradient-text

## 4. SKILLS & TAGS
- A flex-wrap list of skill tags: rounded-full · bg-[#6366F1]/10 · border-[#6366F1]/20 · text-[#818CF8]
- Editable from Profile Settings

## 5. FREELANCER MODE TOGGLE (Conditional)
- Shown only if: accountType === 'student'
- isFreelancer === false: shows "🚀 انضم إلى سوق المستقلين" CTA → /freelance/onboarding
- isFreelancer === true: shows "💼 مستقل نشط" badge + quick link to service management

## 6. DASHBOARD NAV TILES (Inner Sidebar / Tabs)
- 5 navigation items (sidebar on desktop, tabs on mobile):
  1. الملف الأكاديمي → /dashboard (index)
  2. التعلم والدورات → /dashboard/learning
  3. المحفظة المالية → /dashboard/wallet
  4. سجل الطلبات → /dashboard/orders
  5. صندوق الوارد → /dashboard/inbox

## 7. ACTIONS
- PRIMARY: [✏️ تعديل الملف الشخصي] → /dashboard/settings (future)
- SECONDARY: [📤 مشاركة الملف] → copies public profile URL
